I went to a vintage shop and found the perfect rug
Giuseppe knew it was his rug too and he wouldn't get off of it so of course we had to carry the prince up to his room
Giuseppe's middle name is blue so I got him a blue couch but he doesn't like soft plushy things so I got him a cardboard one that's also a scratching post
The color blue is perfect too because it matches with the accents on the carpet
I also painted the wood pieces that are going to become his climbing gym
I really wanted it to blend in with the wallpaper
I got these two vintage frames as well because I didn't want the gallery wall to look like too modern so this blended with the more contemporary frames will be really nice
And unfortunately when installing his climbing gym I need a special drill bit so I guess this is where I leave you guys but I'll be back
